00:21:02,560 --> 00:21:07,920
Never mind. I won't be bothered by it anymore.

288
00:21:07,920 --> 00:21:09,600
Could you please do that?

289
00:21:09,600 --> 00:21:13,660
Just know that I'm saying this because I'm worried about you.

290
00:21:14,680 --> 00:21:17,290
I'll be heading in.

