00:33:00,550 --> 00:33:04,930
Dr. Lee, what's wrong? Are you uncomfortable somewhere?

416
00:33:04,930 --> 00:33:09,440
I... I've lived my life the wrong way.

417
00:33:10,730 --> 00:33:15,950
It hurts so much right here. It hurts, and I regret everything.

418
00:33:15,950 --> 00:33:22,710
Just 30 years. I want to go back 30 years.

419
00:33:22,710 --> 00:33:25,810
I ruined everything.

420
00:33:25,810 --> 00:33:28,780
Why did you live like that?

421
00:33:30,160 --> 00:33:31,750
You idiot!

422
00:33:31,750 --> 00:33:35,190
Idiot...

